		<div class="inner">
			<p>MINBAL is a music production and recording studio owned and operated by Benjamin Balcom in Chicago, Illinois.</p>
			<p>We offer a creative and comfortable environment consisting of four acoustically isolated rooms tied together with connections for audio, MIDI and video signals. MINBAL features a Pro Tools|HD 2 Accel system with 24 channels of Apogee 192k I/O wired into a Quad Eight Ventura console. In addition to Pro Tools we offer analog recording and the studio has a variety of instruments and equipment all of which is available for use during your session.</p>
			<p>Please take a look at our booking information and feel free to contact us if you have any additional questions, would like to inquire about availability or want to set up a time to tour the studio.</p>
