<section class="content-container booking">
	<div class="content-container-body">
		<h3 class="h3">BOOKING</h3>
		<div class="inner">
			<p>Freelance engineers are welcome. Assistants are available for $100/day or $50/half-day.</p>
			<p>Rates are based on 10 hour days. Half-days should run no longer than 5 hours.</p>
			<p>We require a 50% deposit or payment in full to book studio time. A discount will be applied if you choose to pay in full when you book your session. Rates for paying in full are $225 per day or $155 per half-day. We are able to hold dates for a short time in order to confirm potential dates prior to booking.</p>
			<p>Additional fees are charged for use of the tape machines. The fees are $25/day for the use of the Scully 280 and a $15/day for use of the Ampex AG-440. Please notify us in advance if you will need tape for your session or inquire about studio reels for use in tracking basics or for mixdown if you are interested.</p>
			<p>For booking please contact our studio manager Doug Malone: <a href="mailto:doug@minbal.com">doug@minbal.com</a></p>
		</div>
		<aside>
			<ul>
				<li>
					$250 per day
				</li>
				<li>
					$165 per half-day
				</li>
			</ul>			
		</aside>
	</div>
</section>

